title: American Horror Stories Episode 1 The Rubber (Wo)Man Review Part One
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Ryan said in an insta comment that we’ll see many of the og ghosts in the season finale!!!

I was excited for ahs to be back I thought the first episode was good, I just wish we could’ve gotten to see at least a Billie dean cameo but I understand why they couldn’t bring everyone back, I can’t wait to see how the rest of the season goes 😁👍🏽
Oh it’s so nice having some AHS and our queens reviews again!!!!
So glad to be watching one of your recaps, THIS is life returning to normal!  I also loved Paris.  Please consider recapping EVIL.
Loved these episodes so much, probably part 1 a little more but both were great. And The opening credits were amazing! I hope we get a new opening each episode
